monstrated strong leadership for  years at owens corning and his broad financial and international experience will serve the board and our shareholders well we look forward to his contributions to sherwinwilliams for many years” mr thaman has held a variety of senior leadership positions over the course of his career with owens corning he has served as president and chief executive officer since  and chairman since  in addition to his current roles mr thaman served as chief financial officer from  to  president of exterior systems from  to  and president of engineered pipe solutions from  to  he is also a member of the board of directors of kohler company a private manufacturing company and previously served as a member of the board of directors of nextera energy inc a public company and clean energy leader in north america about sherwinwilliams founded in  the sherwinwilliams company is a global leader in the manufacture development distribution and sale of coatings and related products to professional industrial commercial and retail customers the company manufactures products under wellknown brands such as sherwinwilliams® hgtv home® by sherwinwilliams dutch boy® krylon® minwax® thompsons® water seal® and many more with global headquarters in cleveland ohio sherwinwilliams® branded products are sold exclusively through a chain of more than  companyoperated stores and facilities while the companys other brands are sold through leading mass merchandisers home centers independent paint dealers hardware stores automotive retailers and industrial distributors the sherwinwilliams global finishes group distributes a wide range of products in more than  countries around the world for more information visit wwwsherwincom investor relations contact bob wells senior vice president corporate communications and public affairs sherwinwilliams direct  rjwellssherwincom media contact mike conway director corporate communications sherwinwilliams direct  pager  mikeconwaysherwinco